Package com.genesyslab.platform.apptemplate.lmslogger.impl

This package contains internal functionality of LMS Logging and Message Server delivery subsystems.

Note: This package is internal and is not supposed for explicit usage by applications.

  • Interface Summary 
    Interface Description
    MSEventSender
    The anchor point for Genesys Message Server LMS events delivery subsystem.
  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    DirectLmsEventLogger  
    DirectLmsLoggerFactory  
    DirectLmsLoggerFactory.Builder  
    LmsEnumsCache
    Base class for keeping pre-processed annotations information on generated LMS enumerations.
    LmsEnumsProcessor
    Annotation processor for generated LMS enumerations.
    LmsFileData
    LMS file parser.
    It is designed to be internally used in LmsMessageConveyor and LmsEnumGenerator.
    LmsFileData.LmsMessageTemplImpl
    Internal implementation of LmsMessageTemplate for representation of "localized" LMS messages.
    Such message template instances will be created by actual LMS file content in a runtime, and registered in LmsMessageConveyor.
    MSEventSenderImpl
    Default implementation of the Message Server Delivery component.
    MSEventSenderImpl.BoundedDeque  
    SilentLmsEventLogger
    "Silent" implementation of LmsEventLogger.
    All log messages are ignored.
    SilentLmsLoggerFactory
    Implementation of LmsLoggerFactory which produces "silent" LmsEventLogger's.
    SimpleLmsEventLogger
    "Simple" implementation of LmsEventLogger.
    It's to print LMS log messages to stdout.
    SimpleLmsLoggerFactory
    Implementation of LmsLoggerFactory which produces "simple" LmsEventLogger's.
    SimpleLmsLoggerFactory.Builder
